## Zed-Specific Configuration

This file configures Zed's AI assistant integration with Paracle.

### MCP Integration

Zed supports MCP servers. Add to your Zed settings (`.zed/settings.json`):

```json
{
  "language_models": {
    "mcp_servers": {
      "paracle": {
        "command": "paracle",
        "args": ["mcp", "serve", "--stdio"]
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Available Paracle Tools

Through MCP, you have access to 50+ Paracle tools:
- Context tools: `context.current_state`, `context.roadmap`
- Memory tools: `memory.log_action`
- Workflow tools: `workflow.run`, `workflow.list`
- All agent-specific tools

